## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **lecanemab Leqembi 2023** = second FDA Aβ-mAb (accelerated → traditional 2023-07). CLARITY-AD Phase 3 positive (CDR-SB -0.45, 27% slowing). Aβ-protofibril 표적 = aducanumab 의 plaque-only 보다 soluble oligomer 강조. quantum-VQE 의 Aβ-conformer Fab interface 가 직접 fit.
2. **donanemab Kisunla 2024-07** = third FDA Aβ-mAb. TRAILBLAZER-ALZ2 positive (iADRS -3.25, 35% slowing). pyroglutamate Aβ (N3pE) plaque 표적 = lecanemab 와 epitope distinct. plaque clearance 후 dosing 중단 가능 (limited-duration). quantum-VQE 의 epitope selectivity comparator.
3. **aducanumab Aduhelm 2021 → 2024 withdrawal** = first FDA Aβ-mAb (controversial accelerated approval). Phase 3 EMERGE positive + ENGAGE negative 양분. CMS coverage IDE-only. Biogen 2024 voluntary withdrawal. Aβ-mAb era 의 cautionary precedent.
4. **ARIA-E (edema) + ARIA-H (microhemorrhage)** = Aβ-mAb 부작용 cluster (~10-15% Phase 3 lecanemab/donanemab). APOE4 homozygous 위험 ↑↑. MRI surveillance + temporary discontinuation protocol = Aβ-mAb 임상 운영의 핵심.
5. **APOE4 carrier 위험 (Reardon 2024 Nature)** = APOE4 homozygous = 100% AD-by-65 risk paper (Fortea et al). Aβ-mAb 신중 + PGx stratification 필요. cross-pharmacogenomics axis 강결합.
6. **plasma p-tau217 Lumipulse 2024-05** = first FDA-cleared plasma AD biomarker. CSF Aβ42/40 + p-tau181/217 의 blood-based alternative. PET 보다 cheap + scalable. early symptomatic + amyloid+ inclusion criteria 의 gateway. cross-theranostic axis.
7. **brexpiprazole Rexulti 2023** = first FDA AD agitation (BPSD). D2 partial + 5HT2A. 5-decade BPSD off-label (olanzapine/quetiapine + black-box 2005 elderly mortality) 후 first on-label. quantum-VQE D2/5HT2A pocket selectivity.
8. **AChE inhibitor (donepezil 1996 + rivastigmine 2000 + galantamine 2001) + memantine NMDA 2003** = symptomatic 4-drug 25-year era. disease-modifying 가 아니라 cognitive decline 1-2년 delay. Aβ-mAb era 와 병용 가능 (현재 RCT data 한정).
9. **anti-tau mAb (tilavonemab + zagotenemab) FAILED + ASO tau (BIIB080) Phase 1/2** = tau path 는 mAb 실패 + ASO/small molecule 가 next. progressive supranuclear palsy + corticobasal degeneration tauopathy 도 동일 path.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, dementia-specific 임상 의미 한정.

